{"tid":2303763,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"【毋忘初衷】樂隊奮抗強權紛表態","createTime":"2020-11-28T08:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T09:36:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"88039d88a4d4b4bdcc63f31d494e2e70c0fbf4f2","tid":2303763,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:08:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201128/M5Q5HWVFSRDZZJAINCYYPNV2RE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201128%2FM5Q5HWVFSRDZZJAINCYYPNV2RE%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=9578158e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201128%2FM5Q5HWVFSRDZZJAINCYYPNV2RE%2F&h=47cad054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201128/M5Q5HWVFSRDZZJAINCYYPNV2RE/</a><br />\n<br />\n【毋忘初衷】樂隊奮抗強權紛表態<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JRDQOLa2oZAmLfO2MTrQ1zHvI8c=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S5534HVAUNFSDJD6ZXU2QCRC3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJRDQOLa2oZAmLfO2MTrQ1zHvI8c%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS5534HVAUNFSDJD6ZXU2QCRC3A.jpg&h=b6b28df2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLMF<br />\n<br />\nSM近日推出的新歌，被樂迷狠批「封嘴、滅聲」，似有轉軚之勢，但本港仍有不少樂隊組合依然毋忘初衷，繼續無懼表態。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【今非昔比】歌詞由抗爭變包容<br />\n<br />\nLMF<br />\n去年社運期間，於10月曾推出一首《二零一九》，當中歌詞唱出「壞咗响個制度 矛盾邊個製造 腐敗政權企圖謀殺細路」，直接狠批政府霸權及警暴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1xfHGW3oyB_O5bvtOck1gv303dI=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QI6DYWF5EBAKDOUP5A2TC6HDF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1xfHGW3oyB_O5bvtOck1gv303dI%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQI6DYWF5EBAKDOUP5A2TC6HDF4.jpg&h=ccd1d954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRubberBand<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRubberBand<br />\n多年來取態清晰明確，去年社會運動開始，RB將舊歌《天光了》填上新詞為港人打氣，成員泥鯭多次呼籲港人參與遊行，最後他們被內地封殺，歌曲全被下架。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【屢創奇蹟】紅館開騷 四連奪最喜愛組合<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/esxcsepHpSuBfuYLNLOF5TXFslo=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WUXSAN6PTNGO7MRQBCUT2BFH3I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FesxcsepHpSuBfuYLNLOF5TXFslo%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWUXSAN6PTNGO7MRQBCUT2BFH3I.jpg&h=10f4d52d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKOLOR<br />\n<br />\nKOLOR<br />\n去年反修例中林鄭月娥拒絕用「撤回」字眼及道歉言論，主音蘇浩才（Sammy 右二）在社交網站指對她的道歉「唔收貨」，更黑底白字寫着「厚顏無恥」及「下台」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QFcuOw_a000Xhdyvm5k2uHsy4AI=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K6GDYVHS3NHXXPCW6IOWB32R3M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQFcuOw_a000Xhdyvm5k2uHsy4AI%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK6GDYVHS3NHXXPCW6IOWB32R3M.jpg&h=be4e29dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMy Little Airport<br />\n<br />\nMy Little Airport<br />\n一早已立場鮮明，寫過不少以抗爭為主題的歌曲如《宅女，上街吧》、《失業抗爭歌》，去年9月被微博網友舉報，所有歌曲即遭內地音樂平台下架封殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FlL6ISAyNd__vkOwA21cYar_t9c=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TPYKCL6HCFHFREG4CEADWO6CQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFlL6ISAyNd__vkOwA21cYar_t9c%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTPYKCL6HCFHFREG4CEADWO6CQI.jpg&h=f297f207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDear Jane<br />\n<br />\nDear Jane<br />\nDJ雖曾嘲笑：「唱歌都要講政治！」而他們大部份歌曲皆以情歌為主，但四位成員皆在去年6月社運開始時，各自在Ig貼出相片表態，以及留言叮囑上街市民小心。"},{"pid":"414902fecf36686261b2080c640c4a18a949e7bf","tid":2303763,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:12:05.000Z","msg":"達明一派<br />\n<br />\n又唔講"},{"pid":"df03815ebf75a44ee0e451f3e84a14d12761a290","tid":2303763,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:14:20.000Z","msg":"sm無轉軚 一直都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615bece52a73b5961485a127217de3f2592cb766","tid":2303763,"uid":183576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:36:00.000Z","msg":"連親愛的珍都表左態 SM真係執柒左佢啦"}]}